Package: PieGlyph
Title: Axis Invariant Scatter Pie Plots
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R: 
    c(person("Rishabh", "Vishwakarma", email = "vishwakr@tcd.ie", role = c("aut", "cre"),
             comment = c(ORCID = "0000-0002-4847-3494")),
      person("Catherine", "Hurley", role = "aut"),
      person("Caroline", "Brophy", role = "aut"))
Description: This packages helps to replace the points in a scatter plot with pie-chart glyphs showing the relative proportions of different categories. The pie glyphs are independent of the plot dimensions, so won't distort when the plot is scaled.
License: GPL (>= 3)
Encoding: UTF-8
Imports: ggplot2, dplyr, tidyr, rlang, ggforce
Suggests: DImodels, compositions, forcats
